{"id": 1717, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x沃尔沃】这年头，你觉得什么才是真正的“放松”？", "description": "就是那种“一回家就四仰八叉扑倒在床上”的轻松愉快~", "record_count": 8141, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170614103352gPIaGs80fZUrj3Ry.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-15T03:00:07Z", "options": [{"id": 213248, "content": "在无敌海景房阳台晒太阳。在蓝得醉人的高原天空下看云舒云卷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055778}, {"id": 214016, "content": "一个人开车在盘山公路上看风景", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947055}, {"id": 213505, "content": "想象自己放松的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036694}, {"id": 214017, "content": "开沃尔沃V90 CC到瑞典去，找片自然森林，听泉水叮咚作响。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918082}, {"id": 213506, "content": "休息的时候看看恐怖片", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056207}, {"id": 213507, "content": "不用为上班而起床。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012140}, {"id": 213763, "content": "身心通畅的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056660}, {"id": 214019, "content": "开沃尔沃V90 CC到瑞典去，找片自然森林，听泉水叮咚作响。", "image": "img/option/option/20170617234024BV3wtvDC2c1djZ7r", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918082}, {"id": 213508, "content": "放空", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416571}, {"id": 213253, "content": "和喜欢的女孩吃饭看电影，做她喜欢的事，只要和她在一起就放松。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1044024}, {"id": 213509, "content": "和你一起看书   对视一笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056211}, {"id": 213510, "content": "只有我一个人呆着，什么事都不用担心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004451}, {"id": 213255, "content": "安静地和喜欢的人都一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961766}, {"id": 213511, "content": "傍晚躺在海边的沙滩上静静地数着天上的星星，带着耳机听着喜欢的歌，怕海风吹着自己的悠闲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056209}, {"id": 213512, "content": "在火车上，关掉微信，安心睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024500}, {"id": 213513, "content": "下雨天坐在家里的阳台边喝刚做好的咖啡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1032375}, {"id": 213769, "content": "大概，是在我认真的时候吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792035}, {"id": 213258, "content": "思想上的放松才是真正的放松", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649634}, {"id": 214026, "content": "心里不受委屈，想干嘛干嘛呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057729}, {"id": 213259, "content": "雨天躲在家里泡面看片打游戏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720470}, {"id": 213515, "content": "出柜之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034866}, {"id": 214027, "content": "随心所欲画一幅画", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958709}, {"id": 213260, "content": "那天晚上和你在德克士坐着，聊聊以前，聊聊曾经。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940651}, {"id": 213516, "content": "看到工资汇入的短信～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056213}, {"id": 213772, "content": "心里宁静每天都是假期", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056597}, {"id": 213261, "content": "一个人坐在山林里放下一切繁杂只听风声鸟鸣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048929}, {"id": 213517, "content": "财务自由 可以去任何想去的地方 买任何想买的东西 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029425}, {"id": 214285, "content": "自己哭一场后睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130761}, {"id": 213262, "content": "说你就衫姐\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055795}, {"id": 213263, "content": "用了很长时间终于把一件事完整的做完的时候 那一刻的放松", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055798}, {"id": 213519, "content": "泡在浴缸里躺尸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024093}, {"id": 215823, "content": "洗得干干净净的躺床上发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060581}, {"id": 213264, "content": "心灵的自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172153}, {"id": 213520, "content": "睡到自然醒 没有工作没有负担 不用为生活忙碌和担忧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047752}, {"id": 221712, "content": "卸载QQ微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028548}, {"id": 213265, "content": "在安静的地方听音乐，看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838533}, {"id": 213521, "content": "九点五十的晚课，八点多就能完成任务的夏夜", "image": "img/option/option/20170615232102SotPVqbvWRiUlrf8", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056220}, {"id": 213522, "content": "上车先坐一会再出发，停车坐一会再出去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119373}, {"id": 214290, "content": "来一场说走就走的旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058414}, {"id": 214546, "content": "温度适宜，躺床上，听雨声，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987650}, {"id": 213267, "content": "一切按部就班，没有波澜的生活也算一种放松", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246057}, {"id": 213523, "content": "莫名其妙一个人笑出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015887}, {"id": 213268, "content": "高考完", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842703}, {"id": 213524, "content": "早睡早起，悠闲的吃早餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236662}, {"id": 213525, "content": "做人不缺爱，做爱不缺人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948844}, {"id": 214549, "content": "在家里舒舒服服的看些无关利益的书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051107}, {"id": 213270, "content": "考完试看电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910973}, {"id": 213526, "content": "早上将要起床的时候班长通知不用上早自习的那一刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872723}, {"id": 213782, "content": "在自家视野开阔的凉台上读一本书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912040}, {"id": 214294, "content": "和琬儿阿姨在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034969}]}